{"tid":2204717,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"紅色文獻收藏家遭爆竊 大量毛澤東相關藏品被盜 涉40億元","createTime":"2020-09-16T09:14:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T11:53:27.000Z","uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"04c33c85b482ffad61328b4f3e5380fd2efc6396","tid":2204717,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T09:14:28.000Z","msg":"收藏家符春曉油麻地單位遭爆竊 暫未有人被捕<br />\n<br />\n收藏家符春曉在油麻地彌敦道的單位被人爆竊。消息指，大廈保安上星期四晚，發現單位有被人搜掠痕跡，於是報警，證實單位內的字畫和郵票被人偷走，損失金額仍在估算當中，暫時未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n符春曉是內地著名紅色文獻收藏家，收藏大量毛澤東的書法、書信、郵票等收藏品，2018年香港郵學會舉辦郵票展時，符春曉亦有展出收藏品。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2357494\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2357494&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvQFhK%2BZ0PNwQmNlOVL%2F21oE%3D&h=65ceb2d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2357494</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nWtgz6N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnWtgz6N.jpg&h=b8f51abe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f87d861da7fdcdd592a5d33ed52ebef1396f44e1","tid":2204717,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T09:14:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d91b037b6d504c10a21d2b01e2d4de1e8776c0","tid":2204717,"uid":184261,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T09:15:31.000Z","msg":"毛語錄：哪裏有壓迫，哪裏就有反抗"},{"pid":"1342d4ad0ca1d83828a75f24d9a38107f888bc93","tid":2204717,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T09:16:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.hkcd.com/userfiles/1540045676.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcd.com%2Fuserfiles%2F1540045676.jpg&h=72b855aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢話值40億就40億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a62711f096c29d82b72cad9918ed2bfcf5bebf4b","tid":2204717,"uid":313615,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T09:26:09.000Z","msg":"好可能係監守自盜"},{"pid":"ad50efaa604e0373075d46bad84cec1935235e3b","tid":2204717,"uid":42820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T09:27:58.000Z","msg":"擺係大灣區咪無事囉<br />\n香港警察呢排忙緊拉港獨分子執行國安法 治安係差啲架啦"},{"pid":"09e1f3c0e1f538eb079cec51be6a076810eca74f","tid":2204717,"uid":313615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T09:32:19.000Z","msg":"符春曉出生四川，曾任《廣州集郵》雜誌、香港《中華集郵》雜誌主編，現為香港中華文物保護協會副會長及香港郵學會會員。佢主要收集及研究蘇維埃時期的政府文件、郵票、第一次國共內戰時期的文件等，其中更熱衷收集早期毛澤東的書法真迹，包括信件、詩詞及信札，近年佢更在不同刊物上發表對毛澤東書法的研究文章。去年11月，佢更在井岡山舉辦的郵展上，以《世界殿堂看區票》為題，展出多張珍貴郵票及蘇維埃時期的郵票，引起國內收藏家的關注。"},{"pid":"95069f61749ebe617be3602b19cf9cc4fdf73872","tid":2204717,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T10:53:48.000Z","msg":"有冇值40億咁多呀<br />\n乾隆皇咩"},{"pid":"2e2fe2a63b2414f4a0f821eeeee26c6223ca1c47","tid":2204717,"uid":121085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T10:54:54.000Z","msg":"保險 就 fat fat"},{"pid":"5a2a8bcc1b11c7ce4c8dd3b6a21e677fe334292b","tid":2204717,"uid":143230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T11:19:21.000Z","msg":"落去問毛主席再拎過囉"},{"pid":"c5a50fe9782b9193d3bc5dd1fd64e39a3e2f3bad","tid":2204717,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a2a8bcc1b11c7ce4c8dd3b6a21e677fe334292b","tid":2204717,"uid":143230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T11:19:21.000Z","msg":"落去問毛主席再拎過囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T11:53:27.000Z","msg":"講真嗰啲共產主義色彩嘅作品根本冇任何藝術色彩 ，淨係得共匪分子先至對虛無嘅垃圾有所興趣 <br />\n<br />\n利申: 讀緊fine art<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}